## How Reflection Works

1. Read the run history below
2. For each role involved, identify:
   - What worked well (patterns that produced clean handoffs)
   - What got flagged by downstream roles (issues the next role found)
   - Recurring patterns (domain-specific knowledge that keeps coming up)
   - Refined criteria (exit criteria that should be tightened or loosened based on evidence)
